description	"Facility Rodian Sharpshooter

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (2)
- DH-17 Blaster (2)
- Projectile Rifle

^8Attributes:
- Healing (3)
- Reinforcements (1)
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Tracking Darts (3) ^3[CS3]

Given that rodians are typically more precise with weaponry than humans, it made sense for the rodians working at the facility to take the few projectile rifles there were and elect to serve as sniper support against the incoming imperial attack."